main event: On February 9, 1968, a witness observed a luminous yellowish-white kite-shaped object traveling from horizon to horizon in Clewiston, Florida.
interesting points: The object hovered directly overhead before descending,The object did not exhibit any of the typical features of a kite, such as flapping or fluttering,The witness found a round hole where the lens is held burned out,The Air Force was informed and requested further information from the witness,The witness expressed a belief that greater attention should be given to UFO phenomena by the Air Force.
witness description: a civilian who observed the object for 5 to 10 minutes
